Magnolia Low Fat Milk 1L is a nutritious and delicious milk option that offers all the goodness of milk with less fat. This UHT (ultra-high temperature) processed milk is perfect for those looking to reduce their fat intake without sacrificing the taste and essential nutrients found in regular milk. It is enriched with vitamin D and calcium to support bone health, making it ideal for individuals who want to maintain a balanced diet while keeping fat consumption in check. Whether enjoyed on its own, added to cereals, or used in recipes, Magnolia Low Fat Milk is a versatile and healthy choice for all ages.
Type of Milk: Low-Fat UHT Milk
Ideal For: Individuals seeking a nutritious, lower-fat milk option
Ingredients: Fresh cow's milk Calcium Stabilizer Vitamin D3
Storage: Store in a cool, dry place. After opening, refrigerate and consume within 7 days
Where to buy:SM Supermarket Makati, Robinsons Supermarket Pasay
